Name: THERE'S A RIKISHI IN MY HOUSE
About the game: The situation where a Rikishi prohibits you from getting out of your house is one of the worst things that can happen to you in your life. You must escape from your house using things that you have in your house. THERE'S A RIKISHI IN MY HOUSE is a casual escape game. There are 15 multiple endings, and you need about 10 minutes to reach each ending. Please play this game to kill time on a weekend!
